# Frontend Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/frontend.md`**

Key rules:
- Server is source of truth — no business logic duplicated in React
- Use Inertia visits/forms; avoid ad-hoc fetch unless ADR-approved
- Handle loading, error, and empty states in every data-driven component
- Tailwind theme tokens — no arbitrary magic values

